metadata.name: Li was uneasy about the past
metadata.description:
"Master, my time is at an end, farewell..."



"What can teach you, I give you, I hope the master live happy." The sound of the system suddenly came to Li Yixi's mind.



The sudden change made Li Yixi hard to accept.



What do you mean taught me? I haven't practiced yet?



This sudden sound, frighten Li Yixi roar.
